Package: renvvv
Title: Robust 'renv' Package Restore and Update Functions
Version: 0.1.1
Authors@R:
    person("Miguel", "Rodo", , "rdxmig002@myuct.ac.za", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-2036-4878"))
Description: Provides more robust 'renv' restore and update functions that
    continue past individual package failures, retry them individually, and
    report what could not be installed. Unlike the standard 'renv::restore()',
    which stops on the first error, these functions allow the installation
    process to proceed for all packages that can be successfully restored.
